cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.MA

This paper deals with modeling and solving sequential decision making tasks, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of qualitative (or imprecise) information also suggests a connection to data science (cs.DS). The proposed variable elimination algorithm is a common technique in control systems (cs.SY) and optimization (cs.MA).
